## Input

```css
// Unexpected token between modifiers should still allow following modifiers
$color: red foo !global;

// Unexpected token between modifiers should not stop parsing later modifiers
$gap: 1 !default bar !global;

// !important should recover as generic invalid syntax and allow later modifiers
$size: 2 !important !global;

